org.apache.flink.runtime.rpc.messages

类 RemoteRpcInvocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.rpc.messages.RemoteRpcInvocation
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, RpcInvocation

    public class RemoteRpcInvocation
extends java.lang.Object
implements RpcInvocation, java.io.Serializable
    Remote rpc invocation message which is used when the actor communication is remote and, thus, the message has to be serialized.

    In order to fail fast and report an appropriate error message to the user, the method name, the parameter types and the arguments are eagerly serialized. In case the invocation call contains a non-serializable object, then an IOException is thrown.
